snippet.title: Kameo: Element of Power - E3 2005 Trailer (6)
snippet.description:
http://www.newrare.com

This is the E3 2005 trailer of Kameo: Element of Power for the Xbox 360. This game was originally planned for the Nintendo Game Cube, the Rareware left Nintendo and were buyed by Microsoft. Then the game was planned for Xbox but finally finished on Xbox 360.

I do not own this video. No copyright intended.

I'm trying to find some other Rareware/Nintendo old commercials/trailers/promotions so if you find some, you can send me a message please.
